      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0649P0-04541'>
        <a name='S5LV0649P0_20030619_GCR_39'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-filkin' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030619_GCR_39' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Filkin' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
