      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0649P0-04604'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030619_GCR_102' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 9 [<span class="italic">Judge's powers at extradition hearing</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0649P0-04605'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030619_GCR_103' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 60, 60A and 61 not moved.</span>]
