          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030619_GCR_143' title='Link to this speech by Ms Joyce Anelay' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-joyce-anelay" title="Ms Joyce Anelay">Baroness Anelay of St Johns</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
